<span class="headers">Recharging Tinkered Good</span>
<p>
<p><i>(thanks to Kritta)</i></p>

<p>To recharge an item, place item + mana battery in a toolbox (regular, deluxe or summoned via collapsible toolbox) and click combine. No skill is needed (in other words anyone of any race and any skill [even 0] can combine with no risk of failure).</p>

<h4> Rechargeable Items </h4>
<p>
Anizok´s Gauze Press: 20 charges, recharge with mana batttery - class 1 <br />
Anizok´s Maximizing Device: 20 charges, recharge with mana battery - class 6 <br />
Anizok´s Minimizing Device: 20 charges, recharge with mana battery - class 6 <br />
Gnomish Vanishing Device: 5 charges, recharge with mana battery - class 5 <br />
Clockwork Armors (all varieties): 10 charges, recharge with mana battery - class 5 <br />
Happy Dragon: 20 charges, recharge with Saltpeter and Firework (with Blazing Comet effect)<br />
Meterological Rocket: Not Rechargeable </p>

<h4>Battery Sellers</h4>
<p>usually have toolboxes as well. <br />
1,5,6 - Nitram Anizok in Plane of Innovation at loc 1530, 975 <br />
1,5,6 - Nelin Signus in Plane of Knowledge at loc 406, 842, -94 <br />
1,5,6 - Maryalis N'Ryt in Plane of Knowledge at loc 850, 190<br />
1,5 - Adinel Jailbar in Iceclad at loc 4539, 1281 <br />
note: Saltpeter and various mana batteries also drop in Plane of Innovation</p>

<h4>Best Price</h4>
<p><i>(Thanks to Zalla)</i><br />
Mana Battery - Class One = 10pp 5gp <br />
Mana Battery - Class Five = 52pp 5gp <br />
Mana Battery - Class Six = 105pp</p></p><p>
